<p style="text-align: justify;"><span><span><span><span><span>央广网拉萨</span></span><span><span>11月19日消息</span></span><span><span>（</span></span><span><span>记者普布次仁 通讯员</span></span><span><span>苏小三</span></span><span><span>伦珠泽仁）</span></span><span><span>近日</span></span><span><span>，</span></span><span><span>西藏自治区山南市</span></span><span><span>琼结县举行新时代文明实践活动之“践行社会主义核心价值观、寻找新时代最美琼结人”颁奖典礼，隆重表彰一批先进模范人物。</span></span></span></span></span></p>
